Scope and originality
---------------------

This package is an independent implementation with its own narrower
runtime scope. It does not require FPF framework semantics as a whole.
Where needed to preserve the package's own design boundaries, it
intentionally omits or rejects parts of FPF rather than inheriting them
by default.

For the explicit adoption/rejection record, see:

- docs/DECISIONS_REJECTIONS_ADOPTIONS.md
- docs/deep/SOURCES.md
